{"tid":1889630,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 堅持 今日係721 7個月啊","createTime":"2020-02-20T17:14:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T12:17:58.000Z","uid":294614,"like":65,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"904ea4291def05aa71ef4dafc60bf43bf66fc639","tid":1889630,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:14:34.000Z","msg":"今日就係221<br />\n但而家熱門都冇多個post 講<br />\n小弟琴晚開左一個爆咗post <br />\n但係因為<br />\n我係P牌仔開唔到post <br />\n所以而家先可以開多次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當香港人仲掛住排口罩 搶廁紙 討論邊個邊個ig女神<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1887691\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1887691</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n可能大家而家仲喺度慶祝緊有狗中左招<br />\n令到可能會有一班狗集體中招<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係</span></span><br />\n希望聽朝瞓醒之後<br />\n連登熱門會721post 佔大多數<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 唔好忘記 在囚 逃亡異鄉 甚至離開咗我哋嘅手足<br />\n唔好對唔住佢哋嘅犧牲</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2PJuqjv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2PJuqjv.jpg&h=f954df1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5qjUBre.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5qjUBre.jpg&h=0a345c1e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UrTKecV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUrTKecV.jpg&h=27c3af2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0UuUBrf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0UuUBrf.jpg&h=0d53667e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9bg0wZC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9bg0wZC.jpg&h=1eca3ea5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K027bZC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK027bZC.jpg&h=3079b944&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VdP5H6i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVdP5H6i.jpg&h=3e997cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kpHSn6i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkpHSn6i.jpg&h=a63d30b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vxmcn6j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVxmcn6j.jpg&h=c665372d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ty99qjF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fty99qjF.jpg&h=7e8fa910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qSv4YEZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqSv4YEZ.jpg&h=d0b8a51a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vuD99MF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvuD99MF.png&h=a9def47c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UHsnLj0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUHsnLj0.jpg&h=88e802bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我相信 <br />\n香港人 面對武漢肺炎<br />\n仍然毋忘初心</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/ti/NQxSn5G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fti%2FNQxSn5G.jpg&h=0a37f299&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TbVgPLJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTbVgPLJ.png&h=eb6d437c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dAeYiD4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdAeYiD4.jpg&h=bcdd244b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWPpYD4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWPpYD4.jpg&h=9b62be1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求下你哋比我道德勒索一次<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">221<br />\n元朗見</span></span><br />\n大西北人就直接元朗見 <br />\n其他唔喺香港人 唔方便嘅話 各大黨鐵站見<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rt99qhQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRt99qhQ.jpg&h=548deab4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YUTY24v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYUTY24v.jpg&h=812cdd79&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2bExn4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2bExn4w.jpg&h=87ee1516&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n P牌仔 求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望會喺元朗見到你哋</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WNYeF2S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWNYeF2S.jpg&h=988879ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6afe4581013f28b557214c88b6176d01d14455cb","tid":1889630,"uid":294614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:15:17.000Z","msg":"兩push thx"},{"pid":"534fdbeb3ba64207f58fbf116533f9d2b4fe92cf","tid":1889630,"uid":294614,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:15:49.000Z","msg":"唔好忘記 死去嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb61689ef06c562fcdb30a996174629a7724015","tid":1889630,"uid":294614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:16:13.000Z","msg":"P真係好難推得到上去"},{"pid":"dbb3b087c5390a254bf9f7a9ad790f3d31cae869","tid":1889630,"uid":242605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:24:29.000Z","msg":"麻煩各位手足幫手推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n極速訂閱 黃色頻道<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RDORH0t.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRDORH0t.gif&h=6e5e9515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n［黃藍YOUTUBE大戰正式開打］兩大快速壯大黃圈嘅攻略！快啲入嚟幫吓手，極簡單方便方法支持黃YOUTUBER<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1888694\" data-auto-